{"tid":2197022,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"馬德鐘孖囝囝馬在驤騷肌 :P","createTime":"2020-09-10T10:02:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-10T13:39:11.000Z","uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"edfb3532ef6405914d4d518be0f5ceb6feb984e9","tid":2197022,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T10:02:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ldy/20200910/s00009/a6ed6486bbc32b57ca3ba9579844e781.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2F20200910%2Fs00009%2Fa6ed6486bbc32b57ca3ba9579844e781.jpg&h=d1822484&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n馬在驤和爸爸馬德鐘首次以父子擔任代言人，兩父子鬥Chok鬥曬肌。<br />\n<br />\n問馬神如何促成父子檔？他笑言：「本身同品牌合作已經5年，加上大家合作好開心，品牌亦見證囝囝成長，知道他剛好在港，所以促成今次拍攝，一齊做代言拍廣告。（酬勞可觀？）開心價錢。」問到覺得阿仔表現如何？是否覺得他就是自己的翻版？馬神說：「當然滿意，因為是阿仔『處男作』。」 <br />\n<br />\n有「馬神2.0」稱號的馬在驤，拍攝當日舉手投足都Chok到盡，兼且騷弗爆腹肌，不比爸爸馬神遜色。馬在驤表示很高興與爸爸做代言工作，他還向馬神請教擺甫士技巧。<br />\n<br />\n😛"},{"pid":"7d7dd6973e48a5e1ff530a0966027aba5ce794ed","tid":2197022,"uid":5737,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T10:02:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://eastweek.my-magazine.me/tmp_images/article_multimedia_16000/16425/2_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Feastweek.my-magazine.me%2Ftmp_images%2Farticle_multimedia_16000%2F16425%2F2_n.jpg&h=febce927&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5d3471c58d06d889d6c1e05124a2738325b23f6e","tid":2197022,"uid":59929,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T10:04:13.000Z","msg":"啲陰影打到離晒譜"},{"pid":"d50b1951ec4371c932bd6a414bd354ed318cd59c","tid":2197022,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T10:18:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-lax3-2.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.2885-15/e35/s1080x1080/104468188_204543084051403_7548086598906856062_n.jpg?_nc_ht=scontent-lax3-2.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_cat=107&amp;_nc_ohc=lbztr9DXp1oAX_m4TfN&amp;oh=4a8f294b1b58ee3c93e188a176b3b2ae&amp;oe=5F841748\" data-t